				<td colspan="2"><span>A bard for mana for the heal team is kind of a must.  Sucks to be you if you wanna see any action, but someone needs to do it.
<br />

<br />
A bard dedicated to the MT is not a must have unless your MT is rather gimp imo.
<br />

<br />
So any other bards would be paired with the add teams to assist in CCing, adding DPS to your group and the nice to have selo boost as you run to the next spawn.
<br />

<br />
Xegony isn't too bad a fight imo.  The pain in the event is getting the raid force to her.  I liked the Coirinav event the best.  Its intense and fun...you win or lose quickly.  Rathe is da debil.</span></td>
